## â–¶ï¸ How to Run

1. Open either `encryption.ipynb` or `decryption.ipynb` in **Google Colab**.
2. Upload your test image when prompted.
3. Enter the key parameters (a, l, Î±, Î²) manually.
4. View and download the resulting encrypted/decrypted image.

